headline: Moody’s Upgrades Its Outlook on Banks But Flags Deregulation as Risk
summary: The credit ratings firm has a rosier outlook for banks, even as worries about credit quality have grown in recent months.

headline: Wells Fargo & Company Declares Cash Dividends on Preferred Stock
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, November 14, 2025--Wells Fargo & Company (NYSE: WFC) today announced dividends on six series of preferred stock.
